Why do you still read this?  I don't even use this... 

I use http://elizabeth.easyjournal.com  

It has a public comment board now! go post!

Yeah so LiveJournal basically sucks. There's way too much going on. I'm definitely an easyjournal girl.. :) I do have a new journal addy though - so if you want to read my super cool journal - and I know you do, then you better go to Elizabeth.easyjournal.com. Super. IM me sometime... I'm at "Blihz" See ya later.. sucker

Ok. So I have one of these crazy livejournals. I wanted to make this because 1) I was curious as to what the livejournal featuers were.. and 2) there were things that livejournal users could do that I wanted to do too - ex. participate in community journals such as the one for my school. So I up and did it. I do have a regular online journal.. so check it out at http://fiduciae.easyjournal.com. We'll see how much I use this thing. Ciao
